      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "ex:item1",
      "@type": "ex:Item",
      "ex:hasBlank": {
        "@type": "ex:Blank"
      }
    }
  ]
}

We use rdflib a while and used to serialize data to rdf/xml.   There are multiple toplevel graphs in our data, like it is shown in below. There are two "`<rdf:Description rdf:about=…/>`" in the data set…

``` xml
